A '''crackhead''' is a person who is [[drug addiction|addicted]] to [[crack cocaine]]. 

==Usage==
It originally was only used to refer to crack users that are not just desperate to get more crack, but act manic, jittery, and wild, so they stand out even among other crack users. Those labeled as crackheads are also often associated with [[homelessness]].

The term, more recently, has become an [[insult]], to describe anyone who seems to be acting foolishly.